|                          I N S T A L L A T I O N                            |
o-----------------------------------------------------------------------------o

  1) Put the 'cal3d.dll' file of the Cal3D character animation library into
     the 3D Studio MAX directory.
     
  2) Put the 'cal3d_max_exporter.dle' file into the 'plugins' directory of 3D
     Studio MAX.


